{"tid":2430442,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"原來2020年已經有論文講武肺疫苗引起既疾病增強作用","createTime":"2021-03-03T02:47:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T06:26:23.000Z","uid":12599,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5cb13df482f536270c6551689ea92b669af75c01","tid":2430442,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T02:47:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41564-020-00789-5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41564-020-00789-5&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiuhZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=88e85023\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41564-020-00789-5</a><br />\n<br />\nNature係舊年有一篇針對SARS類冠狀病毒(包括武肺)講解Antibody-dependent enhancement (抗體依賴增強)既文章入面, 提及到兩種有可能由疫苗引致既機制, 會令本身既免疫系統面對外來攻擊時失去原有既保護作用<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/05/Antibody_dependent_enhancement.tif/lossy-page1-816px-Antibody_dependent_enhancement.tif.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F0%2F05%2FAntibody_dependent_enhancement.tif%2Flossy-page1-816px-Antibody_dependent_enhancement.tif.jpg&h=dbf0d407&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最簡單既一種情況, 就係打完疫苗後人類免疫系統會random地製造大量既antibody去嘗試中和入侵病毒既表面蛋白, 係成功製造出最合適既抗體前會有部份抗體既一邊(Fc&gamma;受體)係會被自身白血細胞認為係無害既物體而容許進出細胞, 而呢d病毒就會係進入白血細胞後大量增生繁殖, 變相利用一d抗體騎劫左原有既免疫防衛機制, 呢個過程稱為ADE<br />\n<br />\n論文中提到呢種情況係respiratory syncytial virus(RSV, 呼吸道合胞病毒感染), 麻疹, 登革熱, feline infectious peritonitis virus (FIPV, 貓傳染性腹膜炎), H7N9 流感病毒, HIV病毒, SARS同MERS都發現過類似情況, 而武肺係SARS同MERS既近親, 所以有理由相信會有同樣情況發生<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pxxxgTv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpxxxgTv.png&h=32a673b2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另一隻機制係呼吸道內抗體結合外來病毒形成組合物(immune complexes), 繼而引起發炎反應, 導致呼吸道阻塞, 更有可能因此引起嚴重反應<br />\n<br />\n論文結語:<br />\n//Going forwards, it will be crucial to evaluate animal and clinical datasets for signs of ADE, and to balance ADE-related safety risks against intervention efficacy if clinical ADE is observed. Ongoing animal and human clinical studies will provide important insights into the mechanisms of ADE in COVID-19. Such evidence is sorely needed to ensure product safety in the large-scale medical interventions that are likely required to reduce the global burden of COVID-19.//<br />\n<br />\n換做中文即係叫係未做好ADE係武肺出現既情況前, 應該小心平衡兩者既利害關係, 同時應該針對呢個問題做更詳細既動物同臨床研究去了解當中機制<br />\n<br />\n中國疾控中心一早已知武肺有ADE風險, 講明:<br />\n//2020年8月14日，國家藥品監督管理局藥品審評中心發布《新型冠狀肺炎預防用疫苗研發技術指導原則》，其中指出：<span class=\"red\">疫苗研發，安全性是重中之重，疫苗有效性帶來的獲益必須要遠遠高於不良反應帶來的損失，ADE不可接受</span>。//<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sohu.com/a/415876446_114986\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sohu.com%2Fa%2F415876446_114986&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiuhZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=3cce766a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sohu.com/a/415876446_114986</a>"},{"pid":"29a9becf1f34c6c98e3d2654e671676a16e94c76","tid":2430442,"uid":12599,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T02:52:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41586-020-2538-8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41586-020-2538-8&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiuhZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=8a0a96c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41586-020-2538-8</a><br />\n<br />\n另一篇Nature針對武肺AED問題既文章, TLDR, 結論係:<br />\n<br />\n//It is clear that after many years, and considerable attention, the <span class=\"red\">understanding of ADE of disease after either vaccination or administration of antiviral antibodies is insufficient to confidently predict</span> that a given immune intervention for a viral infection will have negative outcomes in humans. //<br />\n<br />\n目前我地對人體接受疫苗後出現AED現像既研究不足, 科學上無法判定有定係無呢個情況。要係小型動物身上做實驗評估同平衡接種疫苗後所得既利益同風險"},{"pid":"823918bd7fa4bbfb754d6a242b12c36b38cf03c1","tid":2430442,"uid":57088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T02:57:03.000Z","msg":"好似好勁，推post先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0695f7324f27f808ef14cd963b7143f420a6be70","tid":2430442,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T02:59:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5946e05dfe0634a0d3530c7f492d551cb91d2ba1","tid":2430442,"uid":172172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T03:04:19.000Z","msg":"疫苗係拎全球人命豪賭一次<br />\n輸咗冚球鏟"},{"pid":"86bfc0456baae87bb46ca63bd644adb19eb58967","tid":2430442,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T03:10:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6267d727b3b47251710287bceeff128570b33cf9","tid":2430442,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T03:35:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0635c0bdf781e98e44abef0ab30371837d801d53","tid":2430442,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T03:58:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"367b8db5f43f0a84b2f958565a86c6633fbfeef2","tid":243